<br>
1 is melle by yerself, 2 is melle in group.<br>
<br>
Dont bother with #1  ehehe<br>
<br>
With melle in group hps dont matter much yer not gonna get taunt. What you will need to do pure damage is a nice low delay wepon and haste. The bigest stat u will need to have high is Attack. You use the low delay wepon cause u will hit more often and thus get the str bonus more. Never saw a real good druid wepon proc. Never use an AoE proc cept for fun. <br>
If you are getting hit AC is king forget hp gear.<br>
<br>
Have fun<br>
